The IBM's Daily Returns

rIBM.Rd

The IBM's Daily Returns

rIBM

Format

A tibble with 3523 rows and 2 variables:

  • date Date. Timestamp information. Daily format.

  • daily_returns Numeric. Value at the corresponding timestamp.

Examples

rIBM
